        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>W1 Classic TwinDos (2021-Current)</h3>
          <p class="model-list">WWH 860 WCS · WWH 660 WCS · WWH 360 WCS</p>
          <p>Mid-tier W1 with TwinDos two-cartridge dispensing (UltraPhase 1 and UltraPhase 2 flacons) and CapDosing for specialty detergents. Adds F211-F214 sensor codes to the standard fault structure. Direct-drive motor, 9 kg (19.8 lb) capacity on some models.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>W1 WXI / WXR Flagship</h3>
